      <scopecontent id="aspace_45f32e135fd43341b3a9279f49483ec0">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, subject files, letters, lists, bulletins, a register, memorabilia, a 16mm film and financial materials documenting the Yale Art Gallery and art at Yale.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
